# template — substitute {{NAME}} with each whip name (noodle, leather, ...)
Output media/{{NAME}}.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 380
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "whip-claude demo {{NAME}}"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
